> Success Response:<br>
> `200 OK`

```json
{
   "error":{  
      "code":"0",
      "description":"request correctly processed"
   },
   "payload":{  
    "paymentToken":"Asjdlfad5543AA33a",
    "paymentID":"0000000001",
    "userRedirect": {
      "href": ""
    }
  }
